"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Project Freedom, which started on Monday, will stop because progress has been made towards a deal with Iran, says the US president. President Donald Trump raised hopes of an agreement between the US and Iran after days of tension.\",            \"english_title\": \"Project Freedom Pauses\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Proyecto Libertad, que empez\u00f3 el lunes, se detendr\u00e1 porque se ha avanzado hacia un acuerdo con Ir\u00e1n, dice el presidente de EE.UU. El presidente Donald Trump levant\u00f3 esperanzas de un acuerdo entre EE.UU. e Ir\u00e1n despu\u00e9s de d\u00edas de tensi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Proyecto Libertad se Detiene\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Two cases of a virus, which rarely spreads between humans, have been confirmed on a ship, and three people have died. Volunteer rescuers aged 78 and 62 died after their boat rolled during dangerous conditions.\",            \"english_title\": \"Virus Cases on Ship\",            \"translated_version\": \"Dos casos de un virus, que rara vez se pasa entre humanos, han sido confirmados en un barco, y tres personas han muerto. Rescatistas voluntarios de 78 y 62 a\u00f1os murieron despu\u00e9s de que su bote se volte\u00f3 en condiciones peligrosas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Casos de Virus en Barco\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A 33-year-old German citizen was detained after an incident, according to the authorities. The explosion is the latest accident in Sutatausa, where another deadly mine disaster happened in 2023.\",            \"english_title\": \"Explosion in Sutatausa\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ciudadano alem\u00e1n de 33 a\u00f1os fue detenido despu\u00e9s de un incidente, seg\u00fan las autoridades. La explosi\u00f3n es el \u00faltimo accidente en Sutatausa, donde otro desastre mortal en una mina ocurri\u00f3 en 2023.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Explosi\u00f3n en Sutatausa\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ilie Bolojan lost the vote after the largest party in his coalition joined the far-right opposition to remove him. He spent much of the race criticizing the state's response to the Covid-19 pandemic led by the Democrat nominee.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ilie Bolojan Loses Vote\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ilie Bolojan perdi\u00f3 la votaci\u00f3n despu\u00e9s de que el partido m\u00e1s grande de su coalici\u00f3n se uni\u00f3 a la oposici\u00f3n de extrema derecha para quitarlo. Pas\u00f3 gran parte de la carrera criticando la respuesta del estado a la pandemia de Covid-19 liderada por el candidato dem\u00f3crata.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ilie Bolojan Pierde Votaci\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Film star Vijay has defied critics to almost win Tamil Nadu polls, marking a change in the political order.\",            \"english_title\": \"Vijay's Political Success\",            \"translated_version\": \"La estrella de cine Vijay ha desafiado a los cr\u00edticos para casi ganar las elecciones de Tamil Nadu, marcando un cambio en el orden pol\u00edtico.\",            \"translated_title\": \"\u00c9xito Pol\u00edtico de Vijay\"        }    ]}"